  "detailed_description": "Godless grove - survival horror game with elements of an open world hunting simulator.<br><br>Adapt to the changing conditions of the grove, learn how to survive, discover the terrible secrets of the locals and overcome the disgusting creatures of evil that filled this forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984000/extras/e59e0e9a5a80380632b3a8e520b911f1.poster.avif?t=1653569142\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984000/extras/e59e0e9a5a80380632b3a8e520b911f1.webm?t=1653569142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984000/extras/e59e0e9a5a80380632b3a8e520b911f1.mp4?t=1653569142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>● The oppressive atmosphere of a dying East Slavic village<br><br>● Get food and resources by hunting. Use decoys, traps and don't make too much noise<br><br>● Fight terrible monsters and find a way to stop them forever<br><br>● High difficulty, the decision to engage in direct combat can cost you a life",
